{
  "stem": "11964.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You don't take any photographs and anything written, because you are, from that moment, you are ceasing to be Polish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You are going to be survivors, Jewish survivors, but not Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they'll tell you, the boys will tell you, the game that you have to play.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Sure enough, we got on the railroad station, and we met them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then they took us over the border to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they told us, once you leave Poland, you are Greek Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we said, why Greek?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because everybody in central Poland, eastern Poland, everybody knows German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People know Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People know French.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People know Dutch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But very few people know Greek.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But since you do have to communicate, so they told us to use gestures, and to communicate by reciting Hebrew prayers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we would talk to each other, and we would say, [SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we would use those Hebrew prayers and communicate by gesturing, when somebody was within earshot of us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took us to Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in Bratislava, we were put in a transit camp, and we would wander around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sure enough, while we were wandering around, we met two people we knew from Radomsko.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then from Bratislava, we waited there for a long time, when they came in, and they said, OK, we are going to the Russian zone of Austria.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took us by train, and we stopped at one location.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the International Red Cross met us there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And somebody obviously said, these are Greek Jews, and they are wandering about on the way back home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of the International Cross people said, oh, we have somebody here who is a Greek, and we will bring them over.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, once the young man heard it, he says, [NON-ENGLISH], let's go.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
